oWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:710,&quot;width&quot;:835,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:213484,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false,&quot;topImage&quot;:true,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F04d02b44-ebfe-49f7-8976-4a688a78d03f_835x710.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F04d02b44-ebfe-49f7-8976-4a688a78d03f_835x710.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F04d02b44-ebfe-49f7-8976-4a688a78d03f_835x710.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F04d02b44-ebfe-49f7-8976-4a688a78d03f_835x710.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" fetchpriority="high"></picture></div></a> <polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></figure></div><p>现在是选举季节，因此病毒式图表快速而激烈地传播，因为双方都试图支持有助于其候选人获胜的经济叙事。在这些尝试，陷入困境，动荡的时期，您基本上是一个聪明的新闻消费者。你不能相信任何单一来源——甚至是我！ - 成为经济趋势和事件的完全公正的解释者。你能做的最好的事情就是在有时间的情况下获取尽可能多的数据，并尝试使用你自己的逻辑和推理能力来弄清楚发生了什么。</p><p>但即使我不能成为您唯一的完美信息来源，我<em>也可以</em>尝试帮助您磨练您的怀疑态度，并认识到您所接受的叙述何时不成立。去年九月，我写了一篇关于如何识别误导性病毒图表的文章： </p><div class="digest-post-embed" data-attrs="{&quot;nodeId&quot;:&quot;0219015e-e8a4-4210-b0fa-7187f3d368ac&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&#8220;The art of any propagandist and agitator consists in his ability to find the best means of influencing any given audience, by presenting a definite truth, in such a way as to make it most convincing, most easy to digest, most graphic, and most strongly impressive.&#8221; &#8212; Lenin&quot;,&quot;size&quot;:&quot;sm&quot;,&quot;isEditorNode&quot;:true,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;How not to be fooled by viral charts&quot;,&quot;publishedBylines&quot;:[{&quot;id&quot;:8243895,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;Noah Smith&quot;,&quot;bio&quot;:&quot;Econ blogger&quot;,&quot;photo_url&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/89fd964a-586f-461a-9f5a-ea4587d45728_397x441.png&quot;,&quot;is_guest&quot;:false,&quot;bestseller_tier&quot;:10000}],&quot;post_date&quot;:&quot;2023-09-13T01:20:51.010Z&quot;,&quot;cover_image&quot;:&quot;https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff9b39106-a033-4d58-9a83-ad16b92bcd89_618x620.jpeg&quot;,&quot;cover_image_alt&quot;:null,&quot;canonical_url&quot;:&quot;https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/how-not-to-be-fooled-by-viral-charts&quot;,&quot;section_name&quot;:null,&quot;id&quot;:136955075,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;newsletter&quot;,&quot;reaction_count&quot;:339,&quot;comment_count&quot;:91,&quot;publication_name&quot;:&quot;Noahpinion&quot;,&quot;publication_logo_url&quot;:&quot;https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F04281755-2cd6-42e5-a496-e69153abebb2_281x281.png&quot;,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false}"></div><p>在我给出的示例中 - 其中包括我在彭博日期张贴的图表！ — 图表中的数据要么不正确，要么以误导性的方式呈现。但是，在许多图表中，基础数据可能是牢固的，而数据的呈现显然并不<em>糟糕</em>，但是人们在图表上附加的叙述不是故事的故事，数据确实在说明。 。</p><p>这是我的《如何不被病毒式图表愚弄》指南第二部分的主题。我将通过研究 2010 年代末经济辩论中非常流行和有影响力的四张图表来说明我的意思：</p><ol><li><p>美国企业学院的“世纪图”</p></li><li><p>经济政策研究所的“生产力与薪酬”图表</p></li><li><p>Lakner＆Milanovic的“大象图”</p></li><li><p>李·德鲁特曼的“政治指南针”图表</p></li></ol><p>但是首先，只是我在说什么的快速示例。前几天，泰勒·妮可·罗杰斯和伊娃·肖<a href="https://www.ft.com/content/f0e38c4d-e875-406d-a61b-78cb7c79a4eb">在《金融时报》上发表了一篇文章</a>，讲述了移民如何在婴儿潮退休潮中帮助维持美国劳动力。他们用图表说明了这一点： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F9da4c87d-7692-4a0f-a501-64b09bb5c2e0_815x733.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F9da4c87d-7692-4a0f-a501-64b09bb5c2e0_815x733.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F9da4c87d-7692-4a0f-a501-64b09bb5c2e0_815x733.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F9da4c87d-7692-4a0f-a501-64b09bb5c2e0_815x733.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F9da4c87d-7692-4a0f-a501-64b09bb5c2e0_815x733.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F9da4c87d-7692-4a0f-a501-64b09bb5c2e0_815x733.jpeg" width="815" height="733" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/9da4c87d-7692-4a0f-a501-64b09bb5c2e0_815x733.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:733,&quot;width&quot;:815,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:81169,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F9da4c87d-7692-4a0f-a501-64b09bb5c2e0_815x733.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F9da4c87d-7692-4a0f-a501-64b09bb5c2e0_815x733.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F9da4c87d-7692-4a0f-a501-64b09bb5c2e0_815x733.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F9da4c87d-7692-4a0f-a501-64b09bb5c2e0_815x733.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div><figcaption class="image-caption">资料来源： <a href="https://www.ft.com/content/f0e38c4d-e875-406d-a61b-78cb7c79a4eb">ft</a></figcaption></figure></div><p>现在，这张图表有一些大问题——它使用了双 y 轴<em>和</em>截断的 y 轴，使得最近的变化看起来比实际要<em>大得多</em>，也很容易让人不经意地误读图表并认为还有更多如今，美国劳动力中的移民人数多于本土出生的美国人。 x 轴也不包括年份，当然它应该包括年份。这些是我在<a href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/how-not-to-be-fooled-by-viral-charts">第1部分</a>中谈到的问题。但是除了这些问题外，许多右翼人士误解了这张图表所讲述的<em>故事</em>。他们不是关于婴儿繁荣退休的故事，而是将其解释为一个关于移民从本地出生的美国人带走工作的故事： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F117d2115-38e3-492e-8c99-1fc927aab2f6_805x757.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F117d2115-38e3-492e-8c99-1fc927aab2f6_805x757.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F117d2115-38e3-492e-8c99-1fc927aab2f6_805x757.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F117d2115-38e3-492e-8c99-1fc927aab2f6_805x757.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F117d2115-38e3-492e-8c99-1fc927aab2f6_805x757.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F117d2115-38e3-492e-8c99-1fc927aab2f6_805x757.jpeg" width="622" height="584.911801242236" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/117d2115-38e3-492e-8c99-1fc927aab2f6_805x757.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:757,&quot;width&quot;:805,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:622,&quot