:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1f3a9f5a-fb0c-4edf-8be3-274ac741e9b3_1318x450.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1f3a9f5a-fb0c-4edf-8be3-274ac741e9b3_1318x450.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1f3a9f5a-fb0c-4edf-8be3-274ac741e9b3_1318x450.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1f3a9f5a-fb0c-4edf-8be3-274ac741e9b3_1318x450.png 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></figure></div><p>换句话说，一张关于婴儿潮退休的图表被误解为一张关于移民就业的图表——在这种情况下，是故意的，并且出于政治原因。数据还不错，但是叙述是错误的。</p><p>无论如何，让我们来获取2010年代的四个著名例子。</p><h4>示例 1：“世纪图表”</h4><p> 1992 年至 2020 年间，美国的通货膨胀率总体较低且稳定。但较低的总体通货膨胀率掩盖了个别商品和服务价格的显着变化——有些东西变得更贵，而另一些东西则便宜得多。在一张通常被称为“<a href="https://www.aei.org/carpe-diem/chart-of-the-day-century-price-changes-1997-to-2017/">世纪图表”的</a>图表中，马克·佩里和美国企业研究所的其他一些人展示了其中一些不同的价格变化。医疗保健、教育和儿童保育都变得更加昂贵，而汽车、服装、家具、电子产品、手机服务和软件都变得更便宜。住房和食物介于两者之间。佩里（现在已退休）最近制作了<a href="https://x.com/Mark_J_Perry/status/1747995005518516419">图表的更新版本</a>，将起点和端点移动一点，但图基本上看起来基本相同，所以我将使用此新版本： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fe3373518-4a44-4e83-b210-e0f092dd391e_900x785.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fe3373518-4a44-4e83-b210-e0f092dd391e_900x785.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fe3373518-4a44-4e83-b210-e0f092dd391e_900x785.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fe3373518-4a44-4e83-b210-e0f092dd391e_900x785.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fe3373518-4a44-4e83-b210-e0f092dd391e_900x785.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fe3373518-4a44-4e83-b210-e0f092dd391e_900x785.jpeg" width="706" height="615.7888888888889" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/e3373518-4a44-4e83-b210-e0f092dd391e_900x785.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:785,&quot;width&quot;:900,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:706,&quot;bytes&quot;:176711,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fe3373518-4a44-4e83-b210-e0f092dd391e_900x785.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fe3373518-4a44-4e83-b210-e0f092dd391e_900x785.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fe3373518-4a44-4e83-b210-e0f092dd391e_900x785.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fe3373518-4a44-4e83-b210-e0f092dd391e_900x785.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div><figcaption class="image-caption">资料来源：<a href="https://x.com/Mark_J_Perry/status/1747995005518516419">马克·佩里</a></figcaption></figure></div><p>这里的基础数据没有问题——它来自劳工统计局。美国劳工统计局并不总是让一切都完美无缺——没有人做到这一点——但他们竭尽全力，而且他们有很多聪明的人不知疲倦地工作，以使这些数据尽可能准确。</p><p>我确实有两个小问题在此图表显示数据的方式。首先，大学学费数字是<em>标题</em>数字，不包括<em>经济援助</em>。学生实际支付大学付费的价格比官方标签价格<a href="https://libertystreeteconomics.newyorkfed.org/2019/06/the-cost-of-college-continues-to-climb/">慢得多</a>，并且<a href="https://www.brookings.edu/articles/college-prices-arent-skyrocketing-but-theyre-still-too-high-for-some/">在2006年之后没有上涨</a>。其次，佩里选择的标签住房和红色标签，因为它们的上升速度比整体通货膨胀率略快，在这里有点怀疑 - 两者都比工资慢，因此它们在这段时间内变得<em>更加负担得起</em>，而不是较少。</p><p>但这些都是小问题。总体而言，这是一个很好的图表，具有良好的数据，它说明了近几十年来美国经济的一个清晰而重要的事实：<strong>物理商品通常越来越便宜，而服务通常越来越昂贵</strong>。</p><p>然而， <a href="https://x.com/search?q=%22chart%20of%20the%20century%22%20government&amp;src=typed_query&amp;f=top">许多看到此图表的人</a>认为，它揭示了服务价格的<em>根本原因</em>提高。他们认为这完全取决于政府的参与和监管： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F2e2eac1a-49b6-4783-ba85-c3f42c8dacc3_914x386.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F2e2eac1a-49b6-4783-ba85-c3f42c8dacc3_914x386.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F2e2eac1a-49b6-4783-ba85-c3f42c8dacc3_914x386.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F2e2eac1a-49b6-4783-ba85-c3f42c8dacc3_914x386.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F2e2eac1a-49b6-4783-ba85-c3f42c8dacc3_914x386.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F2e2eac1a-49b6-4783-ba85-c3f42c8dacc3_914x386.jpeg" width="612" height="258.4595185995624" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/2e2eac1a-49b6-4783-ba85-c3f42c8dacc3_914x386.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:386,&quot;width&quot;:914,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:612,&quot;bytes&quot;:59790,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F2e2eac1a-49b6-4783-ba85-c3f42c8dacc3_914x386.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F2e2eac1a-49b6-4783-ba85-c3f42c8dacc3_914x386.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F2e2eac1a-49b6-4783-ba85-c3f42c8dacc3_914x386.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F2e2eac1a-49b6-4783-ba85-c3f42c8dacc3_914x386.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></figure></div><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa6b847f8-2ba0-4ab5-a492-b46989baa63c_914x356.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa6b847f8-2ba0-4ab5-a492-b46989baa63c_914x356.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa6b847f8-2ba0-4ab5-a492-b46989baa63c_914x356.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa6b847f8-2ba0-4ab5-a492-b46989baa63c_914x356.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa6b847f8-2ba0-4ab5-a492-b46989baa63c_914x356.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa6b847f8-2ba0-4ab5-a492-b46989baa63c_914x356.jpeg" width="610" height="237.5929978118162" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/a6b847f8-2ba0-4ab5-a492-b46989baa63c_914x356.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:356,&quot;width&quot;:914,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:610,&quot;bytes&quot;:78957,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa6b847f8-2ba0-4ab5-a492-b46989baa63c_914x356.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa6b847f8-2ba0-4ab5-a492-b46989baa63c_914x356.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa6b847f8-2ba0-4ab5-a492-b46989baa63c_914x356.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa6b847f8-2ba0-4ab5-a492-b46989baa63c_914x356.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div></div></div></figure></div><p>等等。</p><p>这不是佩里的错。他在 2018 年发布原始图表时<a href="https://www.aei.org/carpe-diem/chart-of-the-day-century-price-changes-1997-to-2017/">表示</a>这只是一种<em>可能的</em>解释：</p><blockquote><p>看到任何图案吗？可贸易品（如电视等进口竞争）与不可贸易品（如儿童保育）、制成品（如服装和汽车等进口竞争）与服务（医疗、医院、教育）、竞争性行业（软件）与受保护行业（医疗保健） ），政府参与/资金/法规的程度？</p></blockquote><p>但是，“政府参与程度”的解释似乎比“可交易，不可交易”和“制造业与服务”的解释更为流行，尽管后者对许多趋势都是完全合理的解释。</p><p>实际上，当我们仔细观察此图表时，我们会看到“政府参与程度”叙述的许多差异。</p><p>大学教科书没有受到严格的监管，但其价格却大幅上涨 - 至少直到2010年代中期。教科书是由廉价学生贷款间接补贴的，但在2009年至2012年政府从私营部门<a href="https://www.mercatus.org/research/data-visualizations/student-loans-held-federal-government">接管</a>学生贷款市场后不久，教科书的价格实际上就<em>停止了</em>上涨。</p><p>手机服务受到严格监管，但其价格却在图表中下降。同时，住房可能是现有最受监管的行业，并且还通过税收减免和代金券通过政府补贴，但其价格在给定时间段的工资少于工资少于工资。</p><p>至于大学学费，私立学校的学费比公立学校高得多，自上世纪九十年代以来，其标价以美元计算的<a href="https://research.collegeboard.org/media/pdf/trends-in-college-pricing-presentation-2023.pdf">涨幅也更大</a>。</p><p>事实上，由于监管和补贴的共同作用而导致服务价格昂贵的流行观念并不能真正作为一个总括的解释。正如我去年在一篇文章中所写，在某些情况下，补贴是问题的一部分，在某些情况下，监管也是问题的一部分，但这里存在大量的细微差别和异质性： </p><div class="digest-post-embed" data-attrs="{&quot;nodeId&quot;:&quot;5a2ca274-a111-4924-9e5e-17c5a878b591&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;In a recent post over at his new substack (which you should check out), Marc Andreessen rails against the exploding prices of big-ticket service industries like college, health care, and child care. He posts the following famous graph from the American Enterprise Institute:&quot;,&quot;size&quot;:&quot;sm&quot;,&quot;isEditorNode&quot;:true,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Why do education, health care, and child care cost so much in America?&quot;,&quot;publishedBylines&quot;:[{&quot;id&quot;:8243895,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;Noah Smith&quot;,&quot;bio&quot;:&quot;Econ blogger&quot;,&quot;photo_url&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/89fd964a-586f-461a-9f5a-ea4587d45728_397x441.png&quot;,&quot;is_guest&quot;:false,&quot;bestseller_tier&quot;:10000}],&quot;post_date&quot;:&quot;2023-03-06T09:57:36.719Z&quot;,&quot;cover_image&quot;:&quot;https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7c6c322c-d9a8-4d47-8374-3eb7cf7beb7d_1024x683.jpeg&quot;,&quot;cover_image_alt&quot;:null,&quot;canonical_url&quot;:&quot;https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/why-do-education-health-care-and&quot;,&quot;section_name&quot;:null,&quot;id&quot;:106662161,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;newsletter&quot;,&quot;reaction_count&quot;:135,&quot;comment_count&quot;:134,&quot;publication_name&quot;:&quot;Noahpinion&quot;,&quot;publication_logo_url&quot;:&quot;https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F04281755-2cd6-42e5-a496-e69153abebb2_281x281.png&quot;,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true}"></div><p> “政府参与”的故事也无法解释为什么许多从 20 世纪 90 年代末到 2010 年代初变得<em>更加难以</em>负担的服务在过去十年中变得<em>更加</em>负担得起： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fbd6b2bae-5452-4375-9584-eb130c234223_900x654.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fbd6b2bae-5452-4375-9584-eb130c234223_900x654.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fbd6b2bae-5452-4375-9584-eb130c234223_900x654.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fbd6b2bae-5452-4375-9584-eb130c234223_900x654.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fbd6b2bae-5452-4375-9584-eb130c234223_900x654.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fbd6b2bae-5452-4375-9584-eb130c234223_900x654.jpeg" width="656" height="476.6933333333333" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/bd6b2bae-5452-4375-9584-eb130c234223_900x654.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:654,&quot;width&quot;:900,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:656,&quot;bytes&quot;:78904,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fbd6b2bae-5452-4375-9584-eb130c234223_900x654.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fbd6b2bae-5452-4375-9584-eb130c234223_900x654.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fbd6b2bae-5452-4375-9584-eb130c234223_900x654.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fbd6b2bae-5452-4375-9584-eb130c234223_900x654.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div><figcaption class="image-caption">资料来源： <a href="https://x.com/jmhorp/status/1750622296283189542">Jeremy Horpedahl</a></figcaption></figure></div><p>因此，尽管几乎可以肯定的是，政府参与在“世纪图表”的某些价格差异中发挥了作用，但这可能只是许多因素之一。正如许多人所做的那样，将图表作为简单的“自由主义者是正确的”叙述的证据是错误的。</p><p>如果这里有一个重要的教训，那就是当图表显示许多不同的趋势时，您应该预期这些趋势有几个不同的原因。很少有“一种经济理论来统治所有这些理论”，如果您认为图表已经证明了这种理论的存在，那么您很有可能会误解图表。</p><h4>示例 2：生产力与薪酬</h4><p>在过去的十年中，也许没有像“生产力与付费”图那样在美国话语中具有影响力。该图有很多版本，但我将使用经济政策研究所发布的版本。这可能是该图表最著名的版本——我们大多数人在 2010 年代末辩论这个问题时使用的版本： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-medi