ers-concerns-eu-election-survey-2024-06-10/">恰恰是因为</a>他们的社会正在变化：</p><blockquote><p> “改善经济并减少通货膨胀”在公民中排名最高，问什么是影响他们投票的最重要的事情，在投票平台Focaldata的一项调查中，与路透社分享……“国际冲突与战争”是第二重要的关注“移民和寻求庇护者”[.]</p></blockquote><p>尽管东欧出现了强劲的追赶式增长，但法国和德国等欧洲核心经济体的生活水平一直落后于美国： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa3e3879d-9ae8-4af8-b460-6dac2dbd1269_1020x731.png" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa3e3879d-9ae8-4af8-b460-6dac2dbd1269_1020x731.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa3e3879d-9ae8-4af8-b460-6dac2dbd1269_1020x731.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa3e3879d-9ae8-4af8-b460-6dac2dbd1269_1020x731.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa3e3879d-9ae8-4af8-b460-6dac2dbd1269_1020x731.png 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa3e3879d-9ae8-4af8-b460-6dac2dbd1269_1020x731.png" width="1020" height="731" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/a3e3879d-9ae8-4af8-b460-6dac2dbd1269_1020x731.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&